        "subject": "LU-1842 mdt: add lvbo support to MDT namespace",
        "message": "LU-1842 mdt: add lvbo support to MDT namespace\n\nWhile inodebits does not require a lvbo, quota locks managed by the\nquota master will need one to manage quota allocation and index\nversion via a LVB. A LVB will also be needed for the layout lock\nsince the LOV EA will be packed in there.\n\nSigned-off-by: Johann Lombardi <johann@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I41a48b8f854d66fdf5d429d7092e0bf9961cf801\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
